thread.title: BRIEF-Zhejiang Busen Garments amends FY 2017 net profit outlook

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Zhejiang Busen Garments amends FY 2017 net profit outlook

organizations.name: reuters) - zhejiang busen garments co ltd

text:
Jan 31(Reuters) - Zhejiang Busen Garments Co Ltd :
* Says FY 2017 net loss at 7 million yuan to net profit at 5 million yuan
* Says in the previous outlook, the company expected the net loss for FY 2017 to be 20 million yuan to 35 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 6.6 million yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/ugrFDS
